	  This buiwds a moduwe which can be watew manuawwy woaded to wun KUNIT
	  test cases against soc-topowogy.c API. This shouwd be pwimawiwy used
	  by devewopews to test theiw changes to ASoC.

	  Do note that it cweates fake pwayback devices which do not intewact
	  weww with usewspace. When wunning tests one may want to disabwe
	  usewspace appwications such as puwseaudio, to pwevent unnecessawy
	  pwobwems.

